果然赞","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_mini.png?m=1477473640","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_normal.png?m=1477473640","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_large.png?m=1477473640","created":1294652197,"last_modified":1477473640},"last_reply_by":"yaoxuwang","last_touched":1666252453,"title":"实在无法忍受 干眼症 和 头痛，决定买一个墨水屏显示器来写代码了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/888366","created":1666237088,"deleted":0,"content":"我这个情况是比较严重的，用几个小时的显示器就会觉得头痛，晚上如果看一个小时的屏幕，就会导致睡不着觉。\r\n\r\n买了“玻璃酸钠滴眼液”来用，缓解了一点点，但还是很不舒服。\r\n\r\n为了好好写代码，我决定买一个 “大上科技 253 墨水屏显示器” 来用，黑白就黑白吧。\r\n\r\n初期研究下来这个显示器刷新速度快，反应灵敏（相对其他墨水屏），就是有点贵。\r\n\r\n难道 V 友们没有这种“病症”吗？ 你们怎么解决的呢？","content_rendered":"<p>我这个情况是比较严重的，用几个小时的显示器就会觉得头痛，晚上如果看一个小时的屏幕，就会导致睡不着觉。</p>\n<p>买了“玻璃酸钠滴眼液”来用，缓解了一点点，但还是很不舒服。</p>\n<p>为了好好写代码，我决定买一个 “大上科技 253 墨水屏显示器” 来用，黑白就黑白吧。</p>\n<p>初期研究下来这个显示器刷新速度快，反应灵敏（相对其他墨水屏），就是有点贵。</p>\n<p>难道 V 友们没有这种“病症”吗？ 你们怎么解决的呢？</p>\n","last_modified":1666237088,"replies":69,"id":888366},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":191592,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3587,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":168296,"username":"summerLast","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/summerLast","website":"weekendproject.space","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"指尖敲击键盘释放出魔法的力量","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35b0/b52c/168296_mini.png?m=1665628685","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35b0/b52c/168296_normal.png?m=1665628685","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35b0/b52c/168296_large.png?m=1665628685","created":1460649145,"last_modified":1665628685},"last_reply_by":"TGl2aWQgIFNC","last_touched":1666252098,"title":"双缝干涉实验的结果说明了什么？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/888332","created":1666233865,"deleted":0,"content":"先说一下我的猜想 \r\n```\r\n1.波由粒子组成\r\n2.波是粒子集合的一个流动形态\r\n3.粒子前进的轨迹是一个旋转（螺旋易于理解）前进的过程\r\n（即粒子根本不是现实中我们理解的走直线；作为单个粒子从发射出去那一刻就不一定是相同的旋转前进轨迹，也就是距离一样旋转轨迹不一样，到达的位置是不同的）\r\n```\r\n-----\r\n\r\n关于观测会导致 斑马线变成两条杆的猜想 ，也许应该用力学去解释，也许这个实验结果本身就是假的","content_rendered":"<p>先说一下我的猜想 </p>\n<pre><code>1.波由粒子组成\n2.波是粒子集合的一个流动形态\n3.粒子前进的轨迹是一个旋转（螺旋易于理解）前进的过程\n（即粒子根本不是现实中我们理解的走直线；作为单个粒子从发射出去那一刻就不一定是相同的旋转前进轨迹，也就是距离一样旋转轨迹不一样，到达的位置是不同的）\n</code></pre>\n<hr/>\n<p>关于观测会导致 斑马线变成两条杆的猜想 ，也许应该用力学去解释，也许这个实验结果本身就是假的</p>\n","last_modified":1666233903,"replies":61,"id":888332},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1664623914","name":"career","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1664623914","title":"职场话题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","topics":13583,"footer":"","header":"这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。","title_alternative":"Career","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1664623914","stars":2483,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":770,"parent_node_name":"work"},"member":{"id":371287,"username":"cheots","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cheots","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e5a2/ebac/371287_mini.png?m=1666233079","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e5a2/ebac/371287_normal.png?m=1666233079","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e5a2/ebac/371287_large.png?m=1666233079","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e5a2/ebac/371287_xlarge.png?m=1666233079","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e5a2/ebac/371287_xlarge.png?m=1666233079","created":1545123923,"last_modified":1666233079},"last_reply_by":"strive","last_touched":1666252495,"title":"校招已经入职实习了，想毁 offer 跑路，该跑吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/888338","created":1666234093,"deleted":0,"content":"之前接了一个小厂的 offer ，要求我正式入职前来实习。今年情况很差嘛，当时也没什么更好的机会，就先来入职实习了。目前还处在学习的阶段，没做啥事情。\r\n最近突然接到了几个本来不抱希望的大厂的 offer ，工资比这边高 40-50%吧，平台也好不少，真的是很难拒绝的条件。\r\n实习这边，同事和 leader 都还挺好的，很难开口，而且也觉得突然跑路很不道德。但是同时也很不想放弃这么好的发展机会。\r\n请问我应该跑路吗？要跑的话还能行吗？会对我之后正式入职别家有影响吗？\r\n\r\nP.S.还没交社保什么的，只签了一份实习生合同（劳务合同），收了一封 offer","content_rendered":"之前接了一个小厂的 offer ，要求我正式入职前来实习。今年情况很差嘛，当时也没什么更好的机会，就先来入职实习了。目前还处在学习的阶段，没做啥事情。<br />最近突然接到了几个本来不抱希望的大厂的 offer ，工资比这边高 40-50%吧，平台也好不少，真的是很难拒绝的条件。<br />实习这边，同事和 leader 都还挺好的，很难开口，而且也觉得突然跑路很不道德。但是同时也很不想放弃这么好的发展机会。<br />请问我应该跑路吗？要跑的话还能行吗？会对我之后正式入职别家有影响吗？<br /><br />P.S.还没交社保什么的，只签了一份实习生合同（劳务合同），收了一封 offer","last_modified":1666234093,"replies":55,"id":888338},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1659331259","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1659331259","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":51435,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1659331259","stars":8034,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":526269,"username":"dcsuibian","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dcsuibian","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c29cba0b0706786011c11a5db6cb8b97?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c29cba0b0706786011c11a5db6cb8b97?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c29cba0b0706786011c11a5db6cb8b97?s=73&d=retro","created":1609345714,"last_modified":1649741364},"last_reply_by":"um1ng","last_touched":1666249851,"title":"4090 装机配置单，麻烦各位老哥帮忙看一下","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/888398","created":1666243805,"deleted":0,"content":"![配置单]( https://dcsuibian-public-resources.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/Xnip2022-10-20_13-03-48.jpg)\r\n\r\n显卡、CPU 没的说。想要 ECC ，所以选的 DDR5 平台。\r\n\r\n显示器目前在 XG32UQ 和 PG32UQ 之间犹豫。XG 目前是 7 千，PG 再贵 500 。前者砍了发光灯、音响（挺好的），96%DCI P3 ，刚出很新。后者原生 10bit （ 4k 120hz 下），98%DCI P3 ，去年 7 月出的。不知道选哪个好。\r\n\r\n机箱和散热完全没主意。想找个亚克力的机箱（钢化玻璃怕爆），但品类很少而且不太好看。想请大家推荐下。","content_rendered":"<p><img alt=\"配置单\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://dcsuibian-public-resources.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/Xnip2022-10-20_13-03-48.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>显卡、CPU 没的说。想要 ECC ，所以选的 DDR5 平台。</p>\n<p>显示器目前在 XG32UQ 和 PG32UQ 之间犹豫。XG 目前是 7 千，PG 再贵 500 。前者砍了发光灯、音响（挺好的），96%DCI P3 ，刚出很新。后者原生 10bit （ 4k 120hz 下），98%DCI P3 ，去年 7 月出的。不知道选哪个好。</p>\n<p>机箱和散热完全没主意。想找个亚克力的机箱（钢化玻璃怕爆），但品类很少而且不太好看。想请大家推荐下。</p>\n","last_modified":1666243805,"replies":38,"id":888398},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":191593,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3587,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":225786,"username":"qzsi001","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/qzsi001","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/30c7/c7e5/225786_mini.png?m=1665453882","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/30c7/c7e5/225786_normal.png?m=1665453882","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/30c7/c7e5/225786_large.png?m=1665453882","created":1492048284,"last_modified":1665453882},"last_reply_by":"gaobh","last_touched":1666252533,"title":"求问，现在买 Xbox Series X 什么版本和渠道会最好？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/888409","created":1666245739,"deleted":0,"co